{
  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><div data-type=\"warning\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"be0a6dd7cc8a5bb32040409b902c0934\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">最聪明的处世术是：既对世俗投以白眼，又与其同流合污。</span></p><p id=\"8b807b71d20dcf5ec9e85b314ceccd6b\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #404040; background-color: transparent\">—— 芥川龙之介</span></p></div><p id=\"d1a363a362e814618a532f53fc752848\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"pEUiC\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">思源笔记 </span><span data-color=\"0\" id=\"Zd2g5\" class=\"ne-label\">我的语雀伴侣🤔</span></h2><div data-type=\"success\" class=\"ne-alert\"><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u31b8a14d\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #EDF9E8\">在</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #EDF9E8\">所有</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #EDF9E8\">文档型双向链接笔记中，只有思源笔记的反向链接能支撑用户实践</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/go/doc/55667507\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/go/doc/55667507\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #EDF9E8\">快速无压的 daily notes 流程</span></a></li><li id=\"ub0f3fc99\" style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/go/doc/31315052\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/go/doc/31315052\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">写作类软件和笔记类软件是有本质区别的</span></a><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #EDF9E8\">，而在</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #EDF9E8\">所有</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #EDF9E8\">笔记类软件中，思源笔记的写作功能是最强的</span></li><li id=\"uc946609c\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #EDF9E8\">在</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/go/doc/16324707\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/go/doc/16324707\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #EDF9E8\">粒度统一</span></a><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #EDF9E8\">这件事上，思源仅次于大纲型的 remnote 和 workflowy，在</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #EDF9E8\">所有</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #EDF9E8\">文档型笔记软件中一骑绝尘</span></li><li id=\"u80a5e8d9\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span class=\"ne-text\">思源笔记的图床功能是</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">所有</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">笔记类软件里对写作者最友好的，既能在线发布又有完全的本地存储</span></li><li id=\"u047895de\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #EDF9E8\">官方同步使用使用 AES-GCM 加密，彻底断绝开发者的偷窥可能性，本地有应用级锁定密码，进一步提升隐私性，在</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #EDF9E8\">所有</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #EDF9E8\">商业笔记软件中思源笔记的隐私性仅次于功能简单的 Standard Notes</span></li><li id=\"ue7bdd045\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #EDF9E8\">懒得继续列了</span></li></ul></div><div id=\"WoFRm\" class=\"ne-bookmark\"><a href=\"https://b3log.org/siyuan/download.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://b3log.org/siyuan/download.html</a></div><h2 id=\"SvnEA\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">滴答清单</span></h2><div data-type=\"info\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"ue160ce1c\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">🐮</span></p></div><p id=\"uddafa078\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/995602/1657037239178-ca25d9ea-f83f-46e9-a017-253921817ac6.png\" width=\"267\" id=\"u9162e49b\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h2 id=\"e5o6x\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">FlowUs </span><span data-color=\"1\" id=\"pWOLh\" class=\"ne-label\">notion-like</span></h2><div data-type=\"warning\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"u8b46e95f\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Notion 用户想找国内替代品可以试试 FlowUs</span></p></div><div id=\"hv5hZ\" class=\"ne-bookmark\"><a href=\"https://allflow.cn/login?code=C3FF0G\" target=\"_blank\">https://allflow.cn/login?code=C3FF0G</a></div><h2 id=\"OXJNA\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">语雀 </span><span data-color=\"2\" id=\"uG3DW\" class=\"ne-label\">🐣</span></h2><div data-type=\"success\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"u4d09bb70\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">不注册语雀怎么关注我呢 🤣</span></p><p id=\"u5e37f807\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果不常用语雀，可以为新通知设置邮件提醒 📩</span></p></div><div data-type=\"warning\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"ubfbe2689\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/login?platform=wechat&amp;inviteToken=d250cce7a9bfb322880f20b1d1c4cdc4fe1c62285a3e5dfcd74c0b19edea4e5b\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/login?platform=wechat&amp;inviteToken=d250cce7a9bfb322880f20b1d1c4cdc4fe1c62285a3e5dfcd74c0b19edea4e5b\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 19px\">点击开始使用语雀</span></a></p></div><p id=\"u021b87f8\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 19px\"></span></p><h2 id=\"mcvvk\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Airtable </span><span data-color=\"4\" id=\"TnU2o\" class=\"ne-label\">多维表格的鼻祖</span></h2><div data-type=\"info\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"u47ab8a09\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">极 度 推 荐</span></p><p id=\"u85c71332\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Airtable 是多维表格真正的鼻祖，功能比模仿品领先很多。国内模仿品可以试试 Seatable。</span></p></div><div id=\"asJHy\" class=\"ne-bookmark\"><a href=\"https://airtable.com/invite/r/g3VtR3Rv\" target=\"_blank\">https://airtable.com/invite/r/g3VtR3Rv</a></div><div id=\"prmjk\" class=\"ne-bookmark\"><a href=\"https://cloud.seatable.cn/invite/link/933f61826ce24dc8bb00efdb5a9dd905/\" target=\"_blank\">https://cloud.seatable.cn/invite/link/933f61826ce24dc8bb00efdb5a9dd905/</a></div><p id=\"uad915c5b\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"sTvuD\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Writeathon </span><span data-color=\"0\" id=\"McWOE\" class=\"ne-label\">真正的卡片写作</span></h2><div data-type=\"danger\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"u72cb39af\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">唯一完整支持卡片模式和双向链接的写作软件，实用性极高，虽然现在很多细节不够完善，但在我心目中的地位已经直追 Scrivener 了，将来把 Ulysses 之流比下去是毫无悬念的。</span></p><p id=\"u1c502760\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><br></p><p id=\"u3e88c666\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Writeathon 有单独的卡片盒功能，它作为一种收集并存储灵感的功能用来代替各种快速记录收集类 APP 也没问题。而且 Writeathon 是一个写作软件，所有卡片能够通过各种功能完美地融入输出流程，所以 Writeathon 的卡片盒不仅仅是个难以整理的堆放处。其实我觉得，一些所谓的“轻量级”笔记软件在知识管理这件事上还比不过 Writeathon 一个写作软件。</span></p></div><div id=\"AKONw\" class=\"ne-bookmark\"><a href=\"https://www.writeathon.cn/register?i=8knvEV\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.writeathon.cn/register?i=8knvEV</a></div><p id=\"u210db434\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"ac534eb2a4bb571f8dc5750b7ff796c3\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Milanote </span><span data-color=\"2\" id=\"iWBu1\" class=\"ne-label\">激发创意的卡片</span></h2><div data-type=\"color4\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"425530098dfad564de2390c36c58e7a5\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">自由灵活的卡片画布工具，让卡片在画布上随意排布，可以不断创建子画布</span></p></div><div id=\"lh28Y\" class=\"ne-bookmark\"><a href=\"https://www.milanote.com/refer/rcCO3ehGRWkqTf3QEE\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.milanote.com/refer/rcCO3ehGRWkqTf3QEE</a></div><p id=\"u3bb7e571\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"cd939ec98090b88d626d925fdbad896c\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Workflowy </span><span data-color=\"4\" id=\"d2e7l\" class=\"ne-label\">一页</span></h2><div data-type=\"success\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"9794f1b655fde9797ce1de8347a87ea3\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">极 度 推 荐。</span></p><p id=\"udc97ff54\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">没用过 Workflowy，不足以谈笔记软件。</span></p></div><div id=\"UWqu4\" class=\"ne-bookmark\"><a href=\"https://workflowy.com/invite/723fe6c3.lnx\" target=\"_blank\">https://workflowy.com/invite/723fe6c3.lnx</a></div><p id=\"560b60fae29f0dc062cc116ea1fc4331\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"26d7c1b78bedd0e182b204d04c888ea9\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">RemNote </span><span data-color=\"5\" id=\"Q8MqQ\" class=\"ne-label\">目前设计得最好的大纲双链笔记</span></h2><div data-type=\"info\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"6ac910775d8c7e0ac8620b3cef9d09b3\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span class=\"ne-text\">remnote 是目前基本设计最佳的大纲型双链笔记软件，roam research 在双链方面理解更深，但综合其它功能来说我觉得 remnote 更好。</span></p><p id=\"u4bc438fa\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span class=\"ne-text\">v1.4 大更新之后，最主要的不足有两个，一是本地化的数据存储做得不够直观，至少跟 obsidian 思源 logseq 之类的软件比起来很不直观；二是中文支持不好（划选搜索和中文标点），根据我的经验，如果一个外国软件的中文支持有问题，基本上是没什么改善希望的——背后的团队再强大、经费再充足也很难改善，因为很多发达国家的开发者根本就无法想象世界上竟然存在不用空格分隔单词的语言。</span></p></div><div id=\"6Q4pl\" class=\"ne-bookmark\"><a href=\"http://remnote.io/invite/86Ta3A3Zf8oFSe3Af\" target=\"_blank\">链接</a></div><p id=\"9817190186283ab66d9b2e831081d749\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"KV1F0\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">葫芦笔记 </span><span data-color=\"1\" id=\"xPrMk\" class=\"ne-label\">roam-like</span></h2><div data-type=\"warning\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"u96184996\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">R2D2 微信机器人收集微信消息很不错</span></p></div><div id=\"RnqIi\" class=\"ne-bookmark\"><a href=\"https://hulunote.com/app?invitation-code=f97e2a80\" target=\"_blank\">https://hulunote.com/app?invitation-code=f97e2a80</a></div><p id=\"u9fa0e56e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><h2 id=\"7ae20da382f425c4822ae92f8679ddc2\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">TeraCloud 云盘 </span><span data-color=\"5\" id=\"De48m\" class=\"ne-label\">日本大容量 webdav 网盘</span></h2><div data-type=\"success\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"38186c80ec37986a031119bd8de6d8c4\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">webdav 网盘可用于 </span><span class=\"ne-text\">joplin，zotero，PDF expert，keepass，tampermonkey</span><span class=\"ne-text\"> 等软件。</span></p></div><div data-type=\"info\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"42b15e6e7a23f36d3f6720c0c71514d9\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">注册登录之后，在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">My Page</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 里输入邀请码 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">8RQ45</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 来获得容量。</span></p></div><div id=\"129cY\" class=\"ne-bookmark\"><a href=\"https://teracloud.jp/en/\" target=\"_blank\">https://teracloud.jp/en/</a></div><p id=\"u1b638235\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p></div>",
  "slug": 16640392,
  "title": "🐑 推荐尝试"
}